r: #0d1117; font-weight: 500;">GitHub Account Settings</strong></li>
                                            <li>Select <strong style=3D"col=
or: #0d1117; font-weight: 500;">Copilot</strong></li>
                                            <li>Choose whether to allow you=
r data to be used for AI model training</li>
                                        </ul>   =20
